data.description: Youre going to love this classic 4 Bed, 3 Full Bath beauty that impresses with a full brick exterior and a welcoming covered porch. Inside, the foyer welcomes you with NEW tile flooring and fresh paint. The open Living Room/Dining Room is perfect for entertaining. The kitchen has been tastefully refreshed with NEW drywall, paint, backsplash, and fixtures, plus a NEW pass-through window with recessed lights overlooking the Sun Room. The Den and Sunroom offer a fresh look with NEW LVP flooring and paint. All 3 bathrooms shine with NEW paint. The basement features a spacious bedroom or den. Enjoy the large open deck with private backyard views and parking options underneath, plus a 2-car garage. Recent upgrades include a NEW ROOF, Drip Edge, and gutters (2023), as well as a NEW Heat Pump (2021) and Furnace (2022). Located just 1 mile from I-65, off Hwy 31, and close to Bill Noble Park. Approx 1.5 miles to downtown Gardendale! 100% financing available! Come make this your forever home!
